<法規內容>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 1</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The Investigation Bureau of the Ministry of Justice establishes the Training Academy (Hereinafter referred to as “the Academy”) to conduct various operational trainings for its special agents and security staff.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 2</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The Academy has one director to handle all affairs relating the Academy. This post is filled by the Director General of the Bureau.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 3</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The Academy has two deputy directors of the recommended or selected appointment rank. One of them works full time. The deputy directors, being answerable to the director, shall assist with affairs relating the Academy.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 4</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The Academy has one secretary of the recommended appointment rank to review documents.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 5</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The Academy has three unit chiefs of the recommended appointment rank to take care of academic affairs, training and general affairs, respectively. Each unit is configured with two to three specialists of the recommended appointment rank, two to three unit members and two to three assistants, all of the designated appointment rank with their respective responsibilities answerable to supervisors.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 6</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Instructors at the Academy, besides part-time instructors paid by the hour, include one chief instructor and two instructors, all of the selected appointment rank or hired through a contract, and three assistant instructors of the designated or recommended appointment rank.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 7</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The Academy is configured with a chief captain of the recommended appointment rank and two captains of the designated or recommended appointment rank to take care of trainees’ daily affairs and management.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 8</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The Academy is configured with one accountant and one personnel manager of the designated appointment rank to take care of accounting, annual budget, statistics, and personnel management, respectively.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 9</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The Investigation Bureau of the Ministry of Justice shall establish training programs and guidelines for the Academy.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 10</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The Statute shall come into force from the date of promulgation.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
</法規內容>
</法規>
